data.description: This gorgeous home has been fully renovated. All NEW everything! Home offers 2 bedrooms on the main floor with a finished lower level that could be a 3rd bedroom or additional family room. Two beautifully updated full bathrooms. The kitchen offers Quartz Countertops, new cabinets and newer stainless-steel appliances. The exterior has a newer roof, new gutters, new cement porch. Newer HVAC and water heater with PEX plumbing throughout home as well as newer windows. Attic is unfinished and perfect for storage or a future owners suite. Nice fenced backyard. There is private parking on the side of home. Why rent when you can buy? Close to downtown with great highway access. Come make this home yours!
